{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1022,"text":"She wrote:"},{"time":2634,"text":"\"When I become famous,\nI will tell everyone"},{"time":5205,"text":"that I know a hero named Marlon Peterson.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":8238,"text":"Heroes rarely look like me."},{"time":10609,"text":"In fact,"},{"time":12058,"text":"I'm what garbage looks like."},{"time":14342,"text":"No, not the most appealing\nway to open a talk"},{"time":17170,"text":"or start a conversation,"},{"time":18891,"text":"and perhaps you have some questions\ngoing through your head about that."},{"time":22388,"text":"Why would this man say\nsuch a thing about himself?"},{"time":24786,"text":"What does he mean?"},{"time":26283,"text":"How can someone view him as a hero\nwhen he sees himself as garbage?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":31253,"text":"I believe we learn more from questions\nthan we do from answers."},{"time":34360,"text":"Because when we're questioning something,"},{"time":36667,"text":"we're invested in taking in\nsome sort of new information,"},{"time":40025,"text":"or grappling with some sort of ignorance\nthat makes us feel uncomfortable."},{"time":44286,"text":"And that's why I'm here:"},{"time":46016,"text":"to push us to question,"},{"time":47575,"text":"even when it makes us uncomfortable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":50269,"text":"My parents are from Trinidad and Tobago,"},{"time":53236,"text":"the southernmost island in the Caribbean."},{"time":55473,"text":"Trinidad is also home\nto the only acoustic instrument"},{"time":58475,"text":"invented in the 20th century:"},{"time":60369,"text":"the steel pan."},{"time":62318,"text":"Deriving from the African drums"},{"time":64735,"text":"and evolving from the genius\nof one of the ghettos in Trinidad,"},{"time":68036,"text":"a city called Laventille,"},{"time":69746,"text":"and the disregard\nof the American military ..."},{"time":73537,"text":"Well, I should tell you,"},{"time":74857,"text":"America, during WWII, had\nmilitary bases set up in Trinidad,"},{"time":78248,"text":"and when the war ended,"},{"time":79693,"text":"they left the island littered\nwith empty oil drums --"},{"time":83253,"text":"their trash."},{"time":84947,"text":"So people from Laventille\nrepurposed the old drums left behind"},{"time":89255,"text":"into the full chromatic scale:"},{"time":91482,"text":"the steel pan."},{"time":93087,"text":"Playing music now from Beethoven\nto Bob Marley to 50 Cent,"},{"time":97495,"text":"those people literally made\nmusic out of garbage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":102754,"text":"Twelve days before my 20th birthday,"},{"time":105277,"text":"I was arrested for my role\nin a violent robbery attempt"},{"time":109172,"text":"in lower Manhattan."},{"time":111001,"text":"While people were sitting\nin a coffee shop,"},{"time":114352,"text":"four people were shot."},{"time":117372,"text":"Two were killed."},{"time":119684,"text":"Five of us were arrested."},{"time":122213,"text":"We were all the products\nof Trinidad and Tobago."},{"time":124875,"text":"We were the \"bad immigrants,\""},{"time":126808,"text":"or the \"anchor babies\" that Trump\nand millions of Americans easily malign."},{"time":131895,"text":"I was discarded, like waste material --"},{"time":134985,"text":"and justifiably so to many."},{"time":137213,"text":"I eventually served 10 years, two months\nand seven days of a prison sentence."},{"time":142205,"text":"I was sentenced to a decade of punishment\nin a correctional institution."},{"time":147966,"text":"I was sentenced to irrelevance --"},{"time":150534,"text":"the opposite of humanity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":153249,"text":"Interestingly,"},{"time":154834,"text":"it was during those years in prison\nthat a series of letters redeemed me,"},{"time":159881,"text":"helped me move beyond\nthe darkness and the guilt"},{"time":162744,"text":"associated with the worst\nmoment of my young life."},{"time":166205,"text":"It gave me a sense that I was useful."},{"time":168938,"text":"She was 13 years old."},{"time":171336,"text":"She had wrote that she saw me as a hero."},{"time":174498,"text":"I remember reading that,"},{"time":175910,"text":"and I remember crying\nwhen I read those words."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179414,"text":"She was one of over 50 students"},{"time":181882,"text":"and 150 letters that I wrote during\na mentoring correspondence program"},{"time":185956,"text":"that I co-designed with a friend"},{"time":187590,"text":"who was a teacher\nat a middle school in Brooklyn,"},{"time":189944,"text":"my hometown."},{"time":191124,"text":"We called it the Young Scholars Program."},{"time":193873,"text":"Every time those young people\nshared their stories with me,"},{"time":197619,"text":"their struggles,"},{"time":199250,"text":"every time they drew a picture\nof their favorite cartoon character"},{"time":203047,"text":"and sent it to me,"},{"time":204506,"text":"every time they said they depended\non my letters or my words of advice,"},{"time":208900,"text":"it boosted my sense of worthiness."},{"time":211841,"text":"It gave me a sense of what\nI could contribute to this planet."},{"time":215508,"text":"It transformed my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":217548,"text":"Because of those letters\nand what they shared with me,"},{"time":220470,"text":"their stories of teen life,"},{"time":222359,"text":"they gave me the permission,"},{"time":224453,"text":"they gave me the courage\nto admit to myself"},{"time":226893,"text":"that there were reasons -- not excuses --"},{"time":229720,"text":"but that there were reasons\nfor that fateful day in October of 1999;"},{"time":234797,"text":"that the trauma associated\nwith living in a community"},{"time":237463,"text":"where guns are easier\nto get than sneakers;"},{"time":240792,"text":"that the trauma associated with being\nraped at gunpoint at the age of 14;"},{"time":247607,"text":"that those are reasons for me"},{"time":250328,"text":"why making that decision,"},{"time":252142,"text":"that fatal decision,"},{"time":253331,"text":"was not an unlikely proposition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256192,"text":"Because those letters\nmattered so much to me,"},{"time":258923,"text":"because writing and receiving"},{"time":260355,"text":"and having that communication\nwith those folks"},{"time":262636,"text":"so hugely impacted my life,"},{"time":264159,"text":"I decided to share the opportunity\nwith some friends of mine"},{"time":267065,"text":"who were also inside with me."},{"time":268485,"text":"My friends Bill and Cory and Arocks,"},{"time":270466,"text":"all in prison for violent crimes also,"},{"time":272714,"text":"shared their words of wisdom\nwith the young people as well,"},{"time":275542,"text":"and received the sense\nof relevancy in return."},{"time":278322,"text":"We are now published writers\nand youth program innovators"},{"time":281532,"text":"and trauma experts"},{"time":283305,"text":"and gun violence prevention advocates,"},{"time":285198,"text":"and TED talkers and --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":286600,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":287650,"text":"and good daddies."},{"time":289128,"text":"That's what I call a positive\nreturn of investment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":292750,"text":"Above all else,"},{"time":293924,"text":"what building that program\ntaught me was that when we sow,"},{"time":297851,"text":"when we invest in the humanity\nof people no matter where they're at,"},{"time":301637,"text":"we can reap amazing rewards."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304991,"text":"In this latest era\nof criminal justice reform,"},{"time":307350,"text":"I often question and wonder why --"},{"time":310992,"text":"why is it that so many believe"},{"time":312549,"text":"that only those who have been convicted\nof nonviolent drug offenses"},{"time":316039,"text":"merit empathy and recognized humanity?"},{"time":321088,"text":"Criminal justice reform is human justice."},{"time":323993,"text":"Am I not human?"},{"time":326880,"text":"When we invest in resources\nthat amplify the relevancy of people"},{"time":331382,"text":"in communities like Laventille"},{"time":332876,"text":"or parts of Brooklyn or a ghetto near you,"},{"time":335049,"text":"we can literally create\nthe communities that we want."}]},{"cues":[{"time":338224,"text":"We can do better."},{"time":339627,"text":"We can do better than investing solely\nin law enforcement as a resource,"},{"time":343239,"text":"because they don't give us\na sense of relevancy"},{"time":346160,"text":"that is at the core of why so many of us\ndo so many harmful things"},{"time":349734,"text":"in the pursuit of mattering."},{"time":353356,"text":"See, gun violence is just a visible\ndisplay of a lot of underlying traumas."},{"time":358443,"text":"When we invest in the redemptive\nvalue of relevancy,"},{"time":361499,"text":"we can render a return of both\npersonal responsibility and healing."},{"time":366304,"text":"That's the people work I care about,"},{"time":368572,"text":"because people work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371313,"text":"Family, I'm asking you\nto do the hard work,"},{"time":375265,"text":"the difficult work,"},{"time":376737,"text":"the churning work of bestowing\nundeserved kindness"},{"time":379696,"text":"upon those who we can relegate as garbage,"},{"time":382167,"text":"who we can disregard and discard easily."},{"time":385023,"text":"I'm asking myself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":387510,"text":"Over the past two months,"},{"time":389454,"text":"I've lost two friends to gun violence,"},{"time":392141,"text":"both innocent bystanders."},{"time":394928,"text":"One was caught in a drive-by\nwhile walking home."},{"time":399100,"text":"The other was sitting in a caf√©\nwhile eating breakfast,"},{"time":402237,"text":"while on vacation in Miami."},{"time":405775,"text":"I'm asking myself to see\nthe redemptive value of relevancy"},{"time":409117,"text":"in the people that murdered them,"},{"time":411699,"text":"because of the hard work\nof seeing the value in me."},{"time":414851,"text":"I'm pushing us to challenge\nour own capacity"},{"time":419009,"text":"to fully experience our humanity,"},{"time":421398,"text":"by understanding the full biography"},{"time":423411,"text":"of people who we can\neasily choose not to see,"},{"time":427908,"text":"because heroes are waiting\nto be recognized,"},{"time":431149,"text":"and music is waiting to be made."}]},{"cues":[{"time":433836,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435128,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}